rows.label: tlk47300163_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Doesn't matter how much we clear up
these pests, they're back before you
know it.

rows.label: tlk47300163_04_msg0003
rows.name:
So I've been thinking about cooking up
some special pesticide to protect the
fields with.

rows.label: tlk47300163_04_msg0004
rows.name:
But getting hold of the ingredients
is a bit tricky...

rows.label: tlk47300163_04_msg0005
rows.name:
I'd need some Uluran Grady ooze and
some fruit...

rows.label: tlk47300163_04_msg0006
rows.name:
I can sort the fruit, no problem. It's
that Uluran Grady ooze that's the
tricky thing...

rows.label: tlk47300163_04_msg0007
rows.name:
Was thinking about getting some mercs
in on the job...

rows.label: tlk47300163_04_msg0008
rows.name:
Oh! You'll go and get some? For me?
What a star!

rows.label: tlk47300163_04_msg0009
rows.name: Just what I need for the pesticide!
